name: White & Brown Combo
description: Elegant and inviting, our white double bed exudes timeless charm. Crafted to perfection, its clean lines and pristine white finish create a soothing ambiance in any bedroom. Paired with a touch of warmth, the brown pillows provide a striking contrast, offering both comfort and style. Indulge in relaxation and sleep in utmost luxury, as this combination seamlessly blends sophistication with coziness for a truly harmonious sleep space.

name: White Forest
description: Elevate your bedroom with our exquisite white double bed. Designed for both comfort and style, this bed offers a spacious and inviting sleeping space for two. The pristine white color exudes a sense of tranquility and sophistication, effortlessly complementing any interior decor. Crafted with attention to detail and quality, this double bed provides a serene oasis for restful nights and a stunning focal point for your bedroom retreat.
